Text: any comments on the quality? looks like a great collection
At 320kbps i think it must be a good Quality

Only listened to Look Sharp! so far and can't say the quality is that great.  There are some light, yet noticeable clicks (pops seems too strong a word to use), but still better than my old (20 some odd years) CD when I try to rip it.  lol
I, on the other hand, have nothing to complain about. Cheers, mate.
